This directory contains shell scripts used to add license header (makeCartouche) 
and to update the version number in this header (updateVersionNumber).
todo: improve this files to automate directory reading ... 


To create a new release: 

Change sed command (lines 13,18 and 20 in updateVersionNumber) to adapt it to the needed number version and title. 
run updateVersionNumber in Numerics, Kernel, Front-End or Sample.
update version numbers in configure.ac (for .so number). 
update ChangeLog file
commit 
remove all .svn files

-> create a tar.gz and upload it on gforge

-> update Siconos download page  (see README in trunk/Web/)

-> update doxygen html pages on gforge, so that they correspond to the published release
	 (directory htdoc/Documentation/Kernel or Numerics_Doxygen on gforge)

-> update dev/design html pages if needed (directory htdoc/docDev on gforge)

